Monday Bar Newsletter week 42 In this newsletter: MONDAY BAR: SISTA NATTEN MED GÄNGET, SATURDAY 18 NOVEMBER • Last Monday Bar party in Stockholm with combo trance, hardstyle, psy och techno • Resident + friends local lineup • Tickets available online and at C.U.M. (cash only) MONDAY BAR CRUISE No 60 JUBILEE, OCT 6-8 • 300 amazing pictures by Timo Torvikoski Dear Monday Bar family, Our Cruise No 60 was just as amazing as we could ever have hoped for. In spite of a bit of a rough sea on our way over to Tallinn, the party and atmosphere was on top on a completely full ship. A testimony of that are all hundreds of comments in our Facebook group, and also Timo Torvikoski’s fantastic (as always) pictures that we have just put up, also on Facebook. There will also be a traditional after-movie later. Now we’re focusing on our next event, Monday Bar: Sista Natten med Gänget, Saturday November 18 at Slakthuset, which will be our last event in Stockholm with the combination of trance, psy, hardstyle, techno, etc that we have become used to of the past +10 years. If and when there will be more Monday Bar land events later, they will be more focused on ”white”. Then there’s the question on everyone’s mind, was this really the last Monday Bar cruise? Well, right now, for different reasons, health, practical, etc, it looks that way, but past experience says "never say never".. so we’ll see if anything changes in the future. But for now, let’s join together in one more fun family gathering on Nov 18. Monday Bar crew 🥰 SISTA NATTEN MED GÄNGET! Lördag 18 november kör vi vår sista fest i Stockholm med den blandning av musik vi har vant oss vid, dvs trance/psy, hardstyle och techno. Om och när det blir några framtida MB-fester så blir det i så fall mer fokus på ”white”. Det finns ju andra arrangörer som är betydligt mer fokuserade på ”black” än Monday Bar. Lineupen på denna sista fest är våra egna residents + vänner. Extra produktion denna kväll. Vi återkommer med speltider lite senare. Lite billigare biljetter finns på C.U.M. Clubwear (cash only) samt online på Billetto. Sedan i dörren i mån av plats. Lineup: ▶ DENISE CAVALLI ▶ DJ ANNELI ▶ CHRISTIAN IONEL ▶ FREDDZ ▶ FREDRIK GRASS ▶ GESTALT ▶ HODEL ▶ JACE HEADLAND ▶ JOHNNY BOY ▶ MINFALK ▶ STETRIX ▶ STEVE ▶ TAVA ▶ TIMPA MONDAY BAR: SISTA NATTEN MED GÄNGET Lördag 18 november, 22.00-03.00 Slakthuset, Slakthusgatan 6, Stockholm T: Globen Ålder 20 år (18 på förköp) Biljetter 200 kr (cash only) på C.U.M. Clubwear, Drottninggatan 81 D Online 250 kr (+ serviceavgift) på Billetto https://billetto.se/e/monday-bar-sista-natten-med-ganget-biljetter-886295 <https://billetto.se/e/monday-bar-sista-natten-med-ganget-biljetter-886295> I dörren 280 kr (i mån av plats) MORE INFO  <https://www.mondaybar.com/monday-bar-sista-natten-med-ganget?ss_source=sscampaigns&ss_campaign_id=653177500def701d3ef5865a&ss_email_id=65317df7d18eba4fabd0dd0f&ss_campaign_name=%F0%9F%9A%80+Monday+Bar+Newsletter+week+42&ss_campaign_sent_date=2023-10-19T19%3A05%3A50Z> NEW PICTURES FROM MONDAY BAR CRUISE No 60 JUBILEE, OCT 6-8, 2023 We’ve just put up over 417 stunning new images by Timo Torvikoski on Facebook. Tag yourself and friends! PHOTOS  <https://www.facebook.com/media/set/?set=a.728587722635221&type=3>  <https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCBTe8_DMsFC3HYqEg4suMxg>  <http://facebook.com/mondaybar>  <http://instagram.com/mondaybar>  <http://twitter.com/mondaybar> © Monday Bar, 1992-2023 Box 2254, SE-10316 Stockholm, Sweden Unsubscribe  <https://campaign-preferences.com/unsubscribe/DDiDaAwA9kerYJqRL0JK9tmeNiA04F8e5zTrRQp7nJgDDIj1vPYVvhtFnVGUM53FET2oO2z2aAbDd-s-n9KcOMvZZakZFp-m7-tL-iXBl_NLc8MHKDA0dDYa8k0OAzhWgEoqKntlP1hG72H8IAkJfG2xlEv8vRNpbhy3Jm3NvoDwMqFjbSKHiBLBERPofSf8ft-9HA4cwWQwNdRDMtMSdq9Shfhi6S156-7TYSSPOXnHavGS5j8fhc3GtpHqdodxnvo0N-QI7KA8fZw4_GgBrmTFhbEsUzknnUF35rJ3GiH4xPbAxDLOzySApIxuflfA3E5npGWQxrWWFzX0tXrsTK8ShpPbmh5Yszg9op_boQIY7bCGJsxnhT0=>